BE NOC — Final Red Flags and Intended Changes

Deliver a single, product-agnostic BE NOC pipeline that assembles the report
from whatever supporting files the scientist uploads. Zero calculations.
Warning-first: block generation ONLY on true structural failure (no files at
all, or every uploaded annexure failed extraction). Placeholder "Not provided."
for empty sections. No "manual review" / warning language in the DOCX body.

