RED FLAG 2 — API name parser fabricates phantom API from dose strings
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Symptom: Product name "Loratadine and Pseudoephedrine Sulfate ER Tablets
5mg/120mg" produces phantom "1.3 120mg" and "8.3 120mg" sub-sections.

Root cause: _parse_api_names_from_product() splits on "and" / "/" and does
