Fix in benoc.py _parse_api_names_from_product():
After the split, add a filter that rejects any candidate matching:
- Pure numeric + unit: r"\d+(?:.\d+)?\s(?:mg|g|ml|mcg|μg|ug|iu|%|units?)$"
