Support salt suffixes: HCl, 2HCl, 3HCl, HBr, hydrochloride, dihydrochloride,
trihydrochloride, sulfate, hemisulfate, bisulfate, mesylate, methanesulfonate,
tosylate, besylate, phosphate, tartrate, hemitartrate, acetate, citrate,
